 EWC.CONNECTED‚Üêconnected
 ‚éïPW‚Üê1000

‚çù NuGrid Demo - Phase 5: Events
‚çù This demo shows CellMove, KeyPress, and Mouse events

 F‚Üê'F1'
 F eWC'Form' 'NuGrid Demo - Events'(50 50)(500 600)('Coord' 'Pixel')

‚çù Create sample data: 4 rows √ó 4 columns of mixed types
‚çù Numbers are automatically right-aligned and formatted with thousand separators
 values‚Üê4 4‚ç¥'Apple' 1500 'USA' 12.99 'Banana' 2500 'Ecuador' 8.79 'Cherry' 500 'Chile' 24.99 'Date' 7500 'Morocco' 3.49

‚çù Column headers
 colTitles‚Üê'Product' 'Quantity' 'Origin' 'Price'

‚çù Row headers (row numbers)
 rowTitles‚Üê1 2 3 4

‚çù Varying column widths: Product=120, Quantity=80, Origin=100, Price=70
 cellWidths‚Üê120 80 100 70

‚çù Create the NuGrid component with headers, sizing, and event handlers
 (F,'.G')eWC'NuGrid'('Posn'(80 20))('Size'(200 400))('Values' values)('ColTitles' colTitles)('RowTitles' rowTitles)('CellWidths' cellWidths)('TitleWidth' 40)('CurCell'(1 1))
 (F,'.G')eWS'Event'(‚äÇ'CellMove' 'CBNuGrid')
 (F,'.G')eWS'Event'(‚äÇ'KeyPress' 'CBNuGrid')
 (F,'.G')eWS'Event'(‚äÇ'MouseDown' 'CBNuGrid')
 (F,'.G')eWS'Event'(‚äÇ'MouseUp' 'CBNuGrid')
 (F,'.G')eWS'Event'(‚äÇ'MouseDblClick' 'CBNuGrid')

‚çù Add instruction labels
 (F,'.Info1')eWC'Label' 'Phase 5: Events - Click cells, use keyboard, see events logged below'(20 20)(20 550)
 (F,'.Info2')eWC'Label' 'Navigation: ‚Üë‚Üì‚Üê‚Üí Tab Enter Home End | Type keys to see KeyPress events'(40 20)(20 550)

‚çù Event log section
 (F,'.LogTitle')eWC'Label' 'Event Log:'(300 20)(20 100)
 (F,'.Log')eWC'Label' '(Events will appear here)'(320 20)(160 550)
